<i>verb</i>: 저하시키다 [저ː하시키다], 우그러지다 [우그러지다], 우그러들다 [우그러들다], 오그라지다 [오그라지다], 오그라들다 [오그라들다], 악화하다 [아콰하다], 악화시키다 [아콰시키다], 악화되다 [아콰되다/아콰뒈다], 동하다 [동ː하다], 덧나다 [던나다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>저하시키다 [저ː하시키다]</dt><br>
<dd>lower; worsen</dd><br>
<dd>정도나 수준, 능률 등을 떨어뜨려 낮아지게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To cause a degree, level, efficiency, etc., to fall and become lower.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>우그러지다 [우그러지다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. dent; become indented</dd><br>
<dd>물체가 안쪽으로 우묵하게 들어가게 되다.</dd><br>
<dd>For an object to bend inward.</dd><br>
<dd>2. shrink; be squelched</dd><br>
<dd>물체의 표면에 주름이 잡히면서 줄어들게 되다.</dd><br>
<dd>For an object to shrink with wrinkles on its surface.</dd><br>
<dd>3. aggravate; worsen</dd><br>
<dd>상황이나 형편 등이 전보다 아주 나빠지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a situation, circumstances, etc., to become much worse.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>우그러들다 [우그러들다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. curl up; dent</dd><br>
<dd>물체가 안쪽으로 우묵하게 들어가다.</dd><br>
<dd>For an object to bend inward.</dd><br>
<dd>2. contract; shrink</dd><br>
<dd>물체의 표면이 주름이 잡히면서 줄어들다.</dd><br>
<dd>For an object to shrink with wrinkles on its surface.</dd><br>
<dd>3. aggravate; worsen</dd><br>
<dd>상황이나 형편 등이 전보다 아주 나빠지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a situation, circumstances, etc., to become much worse.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>오그라지다 [오그라지다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. dent; become indented</dd><br>
<dd>물체가 안쪽으로 오목하게 들어가게 되다.</dd><br>
<dd>For an object to bend inward.</dd><br>
<dd>2. shrink; be squelched</dd><br>
<dd>물체의 표면이 주름이 잡히면서 줄어들게 되다.</dd><br>
<dd>For an object to shrink with wrinkles on its surface.</dd><br>
<dd>3. curl up; be huddled up</dd><br>
<dd>몸이 움츠러져 작게 되다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a part of one's body to be drawn in and become small.</dd><br>
<dd>4. aggravate; worsen</dd><br>
<dd>상황이나 형편 등이 전보다 더욱 안 좋아지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a situation, circumstances, etc., to become worse.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>오그라들다 [오그라들다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. curl up; dent</dd><br>
<dd>물체가 안쪽으로 오목하게 들어가다.</dd><br>
<dd>For an object to bend inward.</dd><br>
<dd>2. contract; shrink</dd><br>
<dd>물체의 표면이 주름이 잡히면서 줄어들다.</dd><br>
<dd>For an object to shrink with wrinkles on its surface.</dd><br>
<dd>3. aggravate; worsen</dd><br>
<dd>상황이나 형편 등이 전보다 더욱 안 좋아지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a situation, circumstances, etc., to become worse.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>악화하다 [아콰하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. worsen; become worse; deteriorate</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 상황이 나쁜 방향으로 나아가다.</dd><br>
<dd>For an incident or situation to proceed in a wrong direction.</dd><br>
<dd>2. worsen; deteriorate</dd><br>
<dd>병의 증세가 나빠지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For the symptoms of a disease to grow worse.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>악화시키다 [아콰시키다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. aggravate; worsen</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 상황을 나쁜 방향으로 나아가게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make an incident or situation proceed in a wrong direction.</dd><br>
<dd>2. aggravate; worsen</dd><br>
<dd>병의 증세를 나빠지게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make the symptoms of a disease grow worse.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>악화되다 [아콰되다/아콰뒈다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. worsen; become worse; deteriorate</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 상황이 나쁜 방향으로 나아가다.</dd><br>
<dd>For an incident or situation to proceed in a wrong direction.</dd><br>
<dd>2. worsen; deteriorate</dd><br>
<dd>병의 증세가 나빠지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For the symptoms of a disease to grow worse.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>동하다 [동ː하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. be aroused</dd><br>
<dd>욕구나 감정 등이 생기다.</dd><br>
<dd>For desire, emotion, etc., to form.</dd><br>
<dd>2. worsen</dd><br>
<dd>나아지거나 나았던 병이 도로 심해지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a disease that was getting better or already cured to become worse again.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>덧나다 [던나다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. worsen</dd><br>
<dd>병이나 상처 등을 잘못 다루어 상태가 더 나빠지다.</dd><br>
<dd>To handle a disease, injury, etc., in the wrong manner, so that its condition worsens.</dd><br>
<dd>2. worsen</dd><br>
<dd>일을 잘못 건드려 상황이 더 나빠지다.</dd><br>
<dd>To handle something in the wrong manner, so that the situation worsens.</dd><br>
<dd>3. annoy</dd><br>
<dd>화난 사람을 잘못 건드려 화가 더 나다.</dd><br>
<dd>To handle an angry person in the wrong manner, so that he/she becomes even angrier.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>